  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1140140/extras/0474b408175f57000ed62c1e89ecdc52.avif?t=1666986233\" width=600 height=75 /></span><br>When Ryuto came back to his hometown from the university during summer vacations, he didn’t expect who he’d meet. Will he have an unforgettable summer? If so, why? You decide!<br><br>A bit different approach to Visual Novel with multiple dating events and endings.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In the game you can:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> take part in some dramas!<br></li><li> go to a summer festival!<br></li><li> end up alone and pathetic!<br></li><li> **** step sister!</li></ul><br>The game has several hours of content (Try all possible, alternative scenarios!)",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1140140/extras/0474b408175f57000ed62c1e89ecdc52.avif?t=1666986233\" width=600 height=75 /></span><br>When Ryuto came back to his hometown from the university during summer vacations, he didn’t expect who he’d meet. Will he have an unforgettable summer? If so, why? You decide!<br><br>A bit different approach to Visual Novel with multiple dating events and endings.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >In the game you can:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> take part in some dramas!<br></li><li> go to a summer festival!<br></li><li> end up alone and pathetic!<br></li><li> **** step sister!</li></ul><br>The game has several hours of content (Try all possible, alternative scenarios!)",
